@wp.kernel
def expr_xkpwfn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v0 = (wp.sin(v2) * wp.sin((v2 + 0.16 / tmp + 0.83)))
    tmp = 0.11
    v1 = (v0 / wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.18)))
    v2 = (0.99 - 0.31)
    v2 = v1
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
